Ok, here we go. <br>
<br>
Barak TR: try to go second so that you can see what hery are playing. once that is acomplished seach whith his command (pulling eather Bragal, Magma Jile, Grater Vaal, or Silth Giant deppending on your situation),(or if your despret you can draw any thing you want, should it be a spell or relic, because u d&#39;ont show the other person) and play your creatures as you see fit. Then this will eather end your tern (saving your Thermal Blast for when you have creatures to target) or play your augresiv spells like Thermal Blast or Brushfire. Save all of your relics for Gar, he will be your savyor. Keep doing this until you dye to set up for your next magi, and save some spells for Ashgar and Gar.<br>
<br>
GO Ashgar: Here is a kikin magi, if you have the Magma Armor play it with him, with his abaty to play a spell if hes attacked you can get a quick t-blast in befor they can kill you n leavin ya with about 7 energy to play with next tern hopefully. play the Krawg n the Quor, savin the Flame Geyser for a possable sewaside if needed.<br>
<br>
Gar: The ever hated straengthener by now u should have a nice aray of creters and relics in your hand and a small amount of spells, just let the berners on full n leave them extra crispy.<br>
<br>
This deck has held its gound for a while agents the #8 world last year a couple times so i figure its worth sharing, and im happy to recieve any sugestions. </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP" COLSPAN="2"><font class="bfont"> <a href="/magination/decks/decks.php">Back to Decks Directory</a> | <A HREF="/magination/decks/decks.php?reviews=24634"> Read Reviews </A> | <a href="deckprint.php?deck=24634" TARGET="BLANK_"> Printer Friendly</a></FONT></TD></TR></TABLE><a name="review"></a><font class="h2font">In order to review decks you must be a registered member. <A href="/magination/main/join.php">Sign up for free!</A></font></td></tr></table></td>
